    "body": "@msmyers sadly that is a limitation of Hardhat's architecture right now. The arguments are not available in the config because we need to resolve the config before knowing all the kinds of arguments that will exist.\r\n\r\nWe've discussed exposing only the \"global\" arguments in the config (`--network` being the most useful one) as a possible solution for this, but we haven't done that yet.",
